---
title: 倉庫選擇流程
description: GitHub 帳號選擇 → 倉庫列表 → 貢獻分析 → 多選確認
links:
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
  - role-system: 角色分類
---
flowchart TD
    Entry([interactiveRepoSelect]) --> Auth{"gh auth status<br/>GitHub CLI 已登入?"}
    Auth -->|"失敗"| AuthFail["請先執行 gh auth login"] --> Exit([退出])
    Auth -->|"成功"| FetchOrgs

    FetchOrgs["取得帳號列表<br/>gh api user → 個人帳號<br/>gh api user/orgs → 組織列表"]

    FetchOrgs --> HasSession{"session 有 org?"}
    HasSession -->|Yes| AutoOrg["自動選擇上次帳號<br/>已連結 xxx · N 個組織"]
    HasSession -->|No| OrgSelect

    OrgSelect{"選擇帳號/組織<br/>上下選擇 · Enter 確認"}
    OrgSelect -->|"AlvinBian 個人倉庫"| Selected
    OrgSelect -->|"組織倉庫"| Selected
    OrgSelect -->|ESC| Back([BACK])

    AutoOrg --> Selected["已選擇：xxx"]
    Selected --> FetchRepos

    FetchRepos["取得倉庫列表<br/>gh api repos · per_page=100<br/>找到 N 個倉庫"]

    FetchRepos --> Contrib["貢獻分析<br/>gh api commits?author=<br/>N 個有貢獻（共 M commits）"]

    Contrib --> RepoList["倉庫列表（按貢獻排序）<br/>1. repo-a 70% · 1336 commits<br/>2. repo-b 16% · 294 commits<br/>3. repo-c 14% · 265 commits<br/>4. repo-d 1 commit<br/>有貢獻的自動預選"]

    RepoList --> Confirm{"操作"}
    Confirm -->|"確認預選（N 個）"| Return
    Confirm -->|"調整選擇"| MultiSelect["smartSelect<br/>Space 切換 · Enter 確認<br/>可選所有 86 個倉庫"]
    Confirm -->|ESC| Back

    MultiSelect --> Return

    Return["返回 repo 物件陣列<br/>fullName, commits, pct, stars<br/>→ 進入角色分類"]

    Return --> RoleLink["角色分類 →"]

    click RoleLink "#role-system"

    classDef decision fill:#d29922,color:#000,stroke:#d29922
    classDef data fill:#1c2128,color:#8b949e,stroke:#30363d
    classDef success fill:#238636,color:#fff,stroke:#238636
    classDef error fill:#da3633,color:#fff,stroke:#da3633

    class Auth,HasSession,OrgSelect,Confirm decision
    class RepoList,Return data
    class Selected success
    class AuthFail error
